{"h0b03c5c2g43eeg490agbd05g7821da2f1c31": ["You! Get me out of this damn thing!", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "8c27cbb5-5037-63d9-c24f-106e924198b0"], "h6250c086g2c0bg4604gb5a9gefc1df87ea7f": ["There is no time. Come.", "201a0ee6-6411-4564-aaea-1ca057bfea04", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "7311bf30-9fa6-615c-f244-0678dfeaf79e"], "h07cd5488gf313g4c3bgad63g09411365ad31": ["Don't waste time on <i>istik</i>. We must go.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "4e6d8429-002e-5602-9e37-801c02c4b994"], "h75018752g766fg4c5fgb529gcd3c9eb99aa3": ["We have no time for stragglers.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "4e6d8429-002e-5602-9e37-801c02c4b994"], "h2893de30gb81cg4085g970fg3c71fbef5055": ["<i>Grip the pod's lid and pull.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "684f7d61-4c15-1389-524d-2c5e82461bf9"], "h9e14f61ag13cag4417g83cfgd6b4575b69bc": ["Enough. Do we go, or do we die?", "201a0ee6-6411-4564-aaea-1ca057bfea04", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "53b4db60-65f9-6a62-5882-d6e48cbac2da"], "ha9d6827dg729dg45d7gbce4ga370770a4fda": ["This ship is crashing. Do you intend to die for a stranger?", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "a8cd9e1c-affb-9529-d65e-bd938adbb0aa"], "h632ab96dg46cdg4172gaf2bgf9580e9571fe": ["<i>We must go. To the helm we must go!</i>", "6ca92237-eb1e-4ed8-a1ee-18b3bef21558", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "a43a4d66-04cc-e8c3-e61d-38cc9157b482"], "h6a5a128cg738fg48abgb2ecgbeb396280b7b": ["Come on, there's got to be a way to open it!", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "6aa90583-bb89-1b29-88be-7dbe134f4db7"], "h97c384dcgd9c7g4927gb259gfa1ccf5498c4": ["<i>Look for a latch that might open the lid.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "de889ae2-bf5a-fcc8-e08a-0ec0bb7afbaf"], "h93f0fed9g0820g411fga53bg19c8866745ff": ["*The construction is too alien. Nothing looks familiar.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "d3e457c3-674f-efdb-01ba-ab80b4fc51fc"], "hb3037a73g1356g4c61gb6dcga322981b500b": ["There's no time - I need to get out of here.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "8d0d0c81-3140-41c7-d7dc-088ea491bbd0"], "h200026acgf479g42bbgb6d4gaa66d89dbe69": ["Wait! Get me out of here, I can help you!", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "06daa898-7f98-5c54-9ea1-76030707bfa5"], "ha309c801g7defg4069gb12egbfd26736ecdc": ["Yes. Come - before it is too late.", "201a0ee6-6411-4564-aaea-1ca057bfea04", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "cb3a6df8-e821-cfdb-dc04-0f6024cfaffc"], "heb56e5acg4ff9g4f82g9998g3d41994c3065": ["Good. Eyes up, and don't look back.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "9f80b65f-30fb-7dea-5136-df5158ed66f9"], "h4f63557egc2f5g4774g8b82ge9d27f782d7f": ["<i>No time. There is no time.</i>", "6ca92237-eb1e-4ed8-a1ee-18b3bef21558", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "c4df7ce4-02f7-24be-2cd3-46ee955ad050"], "hb3840a16gc301g4d59gbfb5g53156650882c": ["If you leave me, I'm dead. <i>Please.</i>", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "978e8c9f-0ebc-7151-5673-cc6977cc0c5f"], "hfddb2595g29feg442fg960cg0253c3ec3c09": ["It's pointless. You're stuck.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "2c4124f2-af45-bb31-4675-11e090f48e7f"], "h5c44c88dgff24g41d8gb66agc71a4fa60d1c": ["You might as well be trapped in Demonwebs. There's no helping you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "2c4124f2-af45-bb31-4675-11e090f48e7f"], "h3210c666g8d6dg46a9g9332g76ba220a9ba0": ["The pod's stuck fast. I can't free you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "2c4124f2-af45-bb31-4675-11e090f48e7f"], "h48ca94f1g6603g4b9eg8ff8g71dff9dd9971": ["Wait! That can't be. There has to be another way. Please!", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "6ade982d-c1f1-87d7-20a1-50b3eaadd737"], "hfc828eddgf75fg4fc8ga796g348ca015d96d": ["We cannot die for one who is already doomed. <i>Come.</i>", "201a0ee6-6411-4564-aaea-1ca057bfea04", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "44fb0c79-0248-e0ea-3fe0-d4737a736859"], "h423d3733g1ca8g48fcg84bfg4fc37f3f2a77": ["It cannot be helped. Come.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "64915224-04af-c91d-f4c8-da04f3fee5cb"], "h61a46d30g1de4g443bg941fge44767a62b25": ["<i>Safe if she stays. Safe if we go.</i>", "6ca92237-eb1e-4ed8-a1ee-18b3bef21558", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "1da37514-5a69-4901-fb96-a1bd550c8b77"], "h080eaab7ga70bg4508g98degb45b5984da91": ["I found some sort of key - it might free you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "dd3c56ba-1702-870e-5dcb-fb1c491fecb0"], "h82acd6a5gf60fg4b2cgb647g290d581b9644": ["Good - try using it on that machine next to me. ", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "04b91e3b-30bb-ee0f-6d59-0203d466c774"], "he09a8952g3a63g4595ga1d3g2b3253e5fac5": ["Hurry! <i>Please!</i>", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "6d396905-124d-1b18-ad88-65bb6a4c4531"], "hd6f3a8cfgc56eg4512gbfb9gd9bc5645a8df": ["This thing's magically linked to that console - let me see what I can do.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "2e66beb1-a942-bb55-6bd3-ea5d20060b93"], "h049ce07dg78c7g4748g9274g246246393164": ["I'll go look around - there must be some way to get this thing open.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "52f4d68c-2250-f598-633f-0fa83a299a03"], "h5d3b2376g3912g4ea1gbcddg96bc7826022b": ["Try that contraption just next to the pod - they did something to it when they sealed me in.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "f91d9c50-93ae-96a0-c38f-0ebb930c8088"], "he5704430g4cabg472fg970bg84025df920de": ["Stay calm - I'll find a way to get this open.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "fbccf3b2-041c-2586-82df-15321ee8aca8"], "h4a64336cgbb6eg437ega186gc7097eee1363": ["Keep looking!", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "f7d76415-527f-4851-2d69-55eedc6f3135"], "h4042bbafg2091g4903ga115g097b9fba1362": ["<i>There's magic at work here. But what kind?</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "546802d2-40fb-dbd5-ac10-c04923d59748"], "h48a952e3g5473g4925gbb3fg5da4b8740391": ["*Warding runes - you feel them drawing energy from the console near to the pod.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "11b1331d-2c6e-e176-4211-c4141a83d6e5"], "h74868b30g433ag425dga3b1g14e24c0c13cb": ["This is madness. We cannot linger here.", "201a0ee6-6411-4564-aaea-1ca057bfea04", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "fa586cf3-c923-e057-7f6b-3ce8aba97b2b"], "h221c6946gcba5g4ac2g90e1g3ad04050bcdd": ["Are you satisfied? We need to <i>go.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "bf19b125-8c34-b00f-60cd-8333140c1f2a"], "h52b70839g7487g42e7ga143g35f4ae34ec46": ["<i>Leave the one, the one must be left! </i>", "6ca92237-eb1e-4ed8-a1ee-18b3bef21558", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "4394b693-f4d7-dcec-4023-085e25717f98"], "h137e537dg5892g41d3ga8d3g4b4e7a74a02d": ["Keep trying! There's got to be <i>something </i>that'll open this!", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "f25efe8e-5a8d-0bb1-c364-7440147d6725"], "h5cce4d8bg54bdg4e87gb666gdd24abaa3d92": ["*The magic's configuration is like nothing you know. Nausea climbs up your throat the longer you try to discern its nature.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "ed95289e-9a8a-6873-4619-cfb66b10cbbe"], "h50b9688fg60c7g498fgbe38g15fea035f2fd": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "485ce2fd-8bd9-eaab-36f4-e53f6839a3be"], "hbc84c169gb616g47fcgb08fge6839cf9e053": ["No! Wait!", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "61ce0856-52da-f47c-4db8-5243c644c097"], "hd8b48b47gd86bg40b2gbec3gf49ae6c881a8": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "a9c80575-fdb4-9828-2f4d-73474b00d5ed"], "h21348428g9516g4bbcg9a86g121a68148661": ["What are you waiting for? Get this blasted tube open!", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "fc511e8b-cf53-229c-83d2-8f50d5a63c90"], "h7ff2c1e6g3ffbg40f1g9a80ga5fc3cc120e5": ["I will <i>not </i>die here. I <i>cannot.</i>", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "ec6a39dd-3a7a-622f-c8d4-ee18e3479e51"], "h8622684ag7b48g44edgb243g196d3bf3ca8a": ["Come on, get me out of this thing!", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "a3b767eb-da15-da1b-c24f-b8387ac3fe2e"], "h1387132eg648fg4b97gaf5fgec7ae6599f34": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Tutorial\\TUT_TransformChamber_PodGirl.html", "e2b798f7-6ac1-2397-d8d6-78c6d3ad7ae9"]}